{"tid":2517394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"非洲馬里25歲產婦誕下九胞胎","createTime":"2021-05-05T09:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T09:45:39.000Z","uid":200298,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"54830a101ffcfbd89f5cb15f91c327305171afed","tid":2517394,"uid":200298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"來自西非國家馬利（Mali）的 Halima Cisse 在進行產檢時，醫生通過超聲波發現肚中有7個嬰兒，由於嬰兒數量太多，為確保她能安全產子，當局立即安排她前往北非國家摩洛哥（Morocco）接受專科治療。<br />\n<br />\nCisse到達摩洛哥後，再照超聲波仍只照出7個嬰兒。沒想到，在剖腹分娩時肚中竟有9個嬰兒，最後Cisse順利誕下9胞胎，分別是5名女孩和4名男孩。<br />\n<br />\n馬里衛生部部長 Fanta Siby 在聲明中指母嬰平安，Cisse和9胞胎健康狀況良好。"},{"pid":"14203334fa5d13a52d1e42e7342712974418cd1b","tid":2517394,"uid":78243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:41:25.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔正仆街"},{"pid":"1c42b4490d7d2563bb8900222d2042deb4dfb011","tid":2517394,"uid":91931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"九等分花嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ada7ae4640e2f886cba6407812ed4bfc98254a8","tid":2517394,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:42:18.000Z","msg":"9個<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefe0fe15177f58822abe9e6a0e257c9e1a1f778","tid":2517394,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"人口爆炸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c87ec47e91f2455d31b84a54d1d6e4f44606edb","